name: Inter Miami
summary: In the 2024 MLS season finale, Inter Miami CF, led by Lionel Messi, hosted the New England Revolution. Inter Miami secured a resounding 6-2 victory, with Messi scoring a hat trick and helping the team achieve an unprecedented record in MLS history. This triumph earned Inter Miami a spot in the FIFA Club World Cup 2025, joining the Seattle Sounders as the only MLS clubs to participate. Messi's hat trick also boosted his personal accolades and solidified his status as one of the greatest players in the world.
